^B@2^Y@3^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|There is some controversy about whether to open 1NT with a balanced 15-17 and a 5 card major. I think the majority consensus is that you should open 1N, and I certainly agree. The problem is, if you open 1S, you have a rebid problem. Let me change my bid to 1S and see what happens.|
